	<br>
	<div style="text-align:right;">
		SAAB, Mansur Paulo Abou<sup>1</sup>; SAAB, Bárbara Maryam Abou<sup>2</sup>; KOTZE, Paulo Gustavo<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
